{
  "stem": "802.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have oranges, bananas, you know, these exotic fruits.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For us, they were exotic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here, they're quite common.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she used to feed us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, she would put us on a window so that we were distracted, in order to eat, because food was extremely important.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because, I guess, my mother, although she came from a very learned family, her father was a writer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He knew several languages, despite the fact that he, or because maybe of the fact that he had a beard and was extremely Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was not a Hasidic, but a very, very Orthodox Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I lost the train of thought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, my mother used to almost take chances with [LAUGHS] our lives in order that we would eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I guess she must have been starving as a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm assuming that, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But food for many Jewish people in Eastern Europe was extremely important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Eating a lot was extremely important, as much as one could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was never concerned about weight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I don't remember too many overweight people, for that matter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not as a result of starvation, but simply maybe the nature of the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Another ploy, another trick to make me eat, was to let me read.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I used to love to read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I would read, then she would shove the food into my mouth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a maid, which was very common.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Virtually everyone did because there were no washing machines or running water for that-- no, we did have cold running water in both apartments.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were no washing machines or dishwashers, so one had to scrub, you know, the-- the washed in that huge-- I don't know what to call it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Polish, it's [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
